      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">

      </li>
  </ul>

  </div>

          
          
          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">We need to make our children proud. We need to reverse the devastating cuts to the NHS. RT our latest election broadcast  <span class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/Mb2yZ6zUL4</span></div>
